reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 29, 2024
reviews.reviewText: This set has everything needed for that special little in your life who loves playing parent! Everything has worked well with my daughter’s wide variety of dolls. It’s also nice that it all fits into the carrying case! Less mess! Perfect for gifting!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 28, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Cute pretend milk &orange juice bottles and sippy cups!!
reviews.reviewText: The media could not be loaded. Great for the little mommy or daddy "feeding" their baby doll. Reminds me of one's I had as a child. Your baby will "drink" all her juice or milk when tipped upside-down/angled. The bottles will refill when turned right-side up. All four work very well. The sippy cups has to be in a certain position to drain properly but not a bug deal. Such a fun pretend play toy! All of the bottles and pacifiers are hard plastic. The baby bottles have a cute baby themed design. The price is great for the quality and quantity of items.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 31, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars My daughter loves them
reviews.reviewText: They look great and work fine. My daughter hasn't put them or her baby doll down all day. Great for the price.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 5, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars great size not too small for 14 month granddaughter
reviews.reviewText: My granddaughter LOVES the magic doll bottles and sippy cup. I am glad I didn't listen to the reviews about being too small. My granddaughter is 14 months and this is prefect size for her little hands. So far it is durable plastic as she has thrown it around many of times. The little pocket book that it came with is coming in very handy for travel. I did take away the pacifiers only because she, herself gave it up months ago and I did not want her to revert back to using a pacifier. When she gets a little older I will reintroduce them as another gift for her " baby doll" !

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 13, 2023
reviews.reviewText: **UPDATE** The seller reached out to me and offered a full refund. Their customer service made me change my review so I'm upgrading this to 4 stars from 2.I bought these a few weeks ago and didn't really inspect them until now since it's time to wrap presents. Well I really wish I would have looked at them closely as one bottle is cracked and it's been leaking this whole time. Ugh so frustrating!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United Kingdom on September 18, 2023
reviews.reviewText: I remember having this myself as a child and being mesmerised how the milk/juice disappeared. Now my granddaughter is just as fascinated by it too. It’s excellent value for money and will keep your little one entertained for hours.
